{"tid":2287441,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"申請Del Post.","createTime":"2020-11-15T18:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T18:19:58.000Z","uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6e16f5c21900d71a9bbbb670c21c9edd21a3f5de","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:30:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2265718/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2265718/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n本來作為遺書po喺連登，<br />\n但係意外被有心人士追擊，<br />\nPost被與貼文無關內容污染，故想Del Post.<br />\n<br />\n唔該幫下手。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6d01a27e955196cf541250796857fe11e16234","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:32:00.000Z","msg":"唔該Del完上邊link嘅post後，<br />\nDel埋呢個Post.<br />\n<br />\nThank you 連登admin so much.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d10f1229301fd6696415caa86683df56cd90c16","tid":2287441,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:37:13.000Z","msg":"咁大個人俾人屌2句就要del Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2574609647bb40af8edea507f953eac96ef5a95","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8d10f1229301fd6696415caa86683df56cd90c16","tid":2287441,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:37:13.000Z","msg":"咁大個人俾人屌2句就要del Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:38:55.000Z","msg":"哈，我話左主要原因係因為post被污染。<br />\n想Del Po係我自由。<br />\n關你柒事。<br />\n<br />\n喺網上攻擊一個現實層面嘅精神病患可以令你拎到咩滿足感？<br />\n睇嚟你同佢同樣無聊至極。"},{"pid":"878ffce6b7b0284419ed913cbfdc0b3f6a8bb2e6","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d10f1229301fd6696415caa86683df56cd90c16","tid":2287441,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:37:13.000Z","msg":"咁大個人俾人屌2句就要del Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:40:42.000Z","msg":"喺連登我同大把人對過線，<br />\n同嗰位叫濟癲嘅對到凌晨五點半我都冇話要Del Acc.<br />\n<br />\n想Del po單純係因為遺書被無關評論污染。<br />\n唔信罷就，你信唔信我都冇賺。"},{"pid":"5423a0989b5f5d01c862e9ab6f39ba41a88506e1","tid":2287441,"uid":308264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:45:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09e33ff742df80765432914b4cae8ce5b6288ce7","tid":2287441,"uid":308264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:46:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96c0b8c20e02f4acfc2bdd10af51550a91a83d0e","tid":2287441,"uid":367299,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:47:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d85520ac435a8a248404a76df502c1da98ceea68","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96c0b8c20e02f4acfc2bdd10af51550a91a83d0e","tid":2287441,"uid":367299,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a2574609647bb40af8edea507f953eac96ef5a95","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8d10f1229301fd6696415caa86683df56cd90c16","tid":2287441,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:37:13.000Z","msg":"咁大個人俾人屌2句就要del Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:38:55.000Z","msg":"哈，我話左主要原因係因為post被污染。<br />\n想Del Po係我自由。<br />\n關你柒事。<br />\n<br />\n喺網上攻擊一個現實層面嘅精神病患可以令你拎到咩滿足感？<br />\n睇嚟你同佢同樣無聊至極。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:47:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:52:50.000Z","msg":"哈，你點睇我都無所謂。<br />\n入邊條link張圖佢咪起左我底囉。<br />\n嗰句節錄就係我嘅動機。<br />\n<br />\n可能係想被安慰，<br />\n可能係想要有全新嘅奇跡，<br />\n可能係想被肆意踐踏嚟使我嘅死志更堅定。<br />\n<br />\n自從九月開始，我已經做事再冇任何動機。<br />\n或者話已經放棄思考自己嘅動機，將所有嘢交畀當下嘅心情去做。<br />\n將一切都放空，交畀無意識。<br />\n有時甚至連自己係邊個，上一秒諗緊咩都唔記得。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n不過而家點解會覆你嘅動機，我知道呢。<br />\n因為反正呢個post，連登admin正常都會幫手del.<br />\n唔會留底就畀我自顧自咁講兩句罷。"},{"pid":"b57ea8d25d0b4f33d9a2b27520b7a15ce7b9a745","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5423a0989b5f5d01c862e9ab6f39ba41a88506e1","tid":2287441,"uid":308264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:45:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T19:00:14.000Z","msg":"Thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登有愛嘅體現者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93457f4db74ffee4e5fe1741af2f9269abee4058","tid":2287441,"uid":308264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T19:01:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1915e60fa76a3767c0d7528186a399a0c39ff718","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93457f4db74ffee4e5fe1741af2f9269abee4058","tid":2287441,"uid":308264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b57ea8d25d0b4f33d9a2b27520b7a15ce7b9a745","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5423a0989b5f5d01c862e9ab6f39ba41a88506e1","tid":2287441,"uid":308264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:45:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T19:00:14.000Z","msg":"Thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登有愛嘅體現者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T19:01:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T19:05:51.000Z","msg":"...我其實無所謂。<br />\n或者話我自己都唔係聖人，有可以被捉住攻訐嘅地方太正常。<br />\n<br />\n會介意嘅話，我不如一開始就唔好註冊發言好過。<br />\n作為自冠乖僻張狂一系列惡名嘅癲佬，反而相當樂於同人地對線呢。<br />\n只不過喺遺言上，呢種偏離主題嘅內容實在污染主題。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n只不過都係要多謝你嘅些少關心。<br />\n願你得到你一生中所體現嘅善，與之等量嘅幸福。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab528ece24ebdfed54d0511cfde257d14646e2c","tid":2287441,"uid":308264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T19:09:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33c36ce89c42af6c38d5e151cb696f51cc8c08da","tid":2287441,"uid":367299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T21:11:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51d6ca4fd36e86372c61353981e6bab2c8026bb6","tid":2287441,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T23:47:53.000Z","msg":"封遺書長到好似作文咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640e35f030671fa2175d556254017231118d1abb","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33c36ce89c42af6c38d5e151cb696f51cc8c08da","tid":2287441,"uid":367299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T21:11:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"Yes, any problem? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025f200597beca2718f627d920c4b015cf0b5702","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51d6ca4fd36e86372c61353981e6bab2c8026bb6","tid":2287441,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T23:47:53.000Z","msg":"封遺書長到好似作文咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本來有七大段㗎，未po曬姐。<br />\n齋草稿打左成六、七個鐘。<br />\n冇人話過遺書唔可以寫曬成世人所有內容喎。<br />\n<br />\n唔通我都要死啦，連遺書都要受人限制？"},{"pid":"e790c71e87013a05237cc09bd0a4eb55c4b13efb","tid":2287441,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:13:29